text: Who let you in?
Glad I brought my ear plugs.
Oh... it’s *you* again.
Don’t you have anything better to do?
Wow, someone’s desperate for attention.
Great, you’re back. Just what we needed.
Ugh. You again?
What now?
I was having a good day, then you showed up.
Look who crawled out from under a rock.
Back for more, huh?
I didn’t ask for your presence.
Oh great. *This* guy.
Go touch some grass.
You’re like a recurring rash.
I thought we banned you.
I’d say welcome back, but I’d be lying.
Can we pretend you’re not here?
Surprised your keyboard still works.
Your internet didn’t do us the favor today, huh?
Guess who just ruined the vibe?
Wonderful. Just wonderful.
Every time you show up, a brain cell dies.
You sure you want to embarrass yourself again?
That awkward moment when you think we missed you.
Quick! Someone act like we care.
Please let this be quick.
